  "rule_text": "The Gradient Callout CTA is a full-width banner with a headline and a single button both horizontally centered and stacked over the branded orange/yellow gradient background image (600px full content width). The headline sits in the top third: Brand Blue (#00529b), centered, Nunito Sans weight 800, ~28px, one line. The button sits in the lower-middle below the headline: Deep Blue (#003D74) fill, white Nunito Sans 800 18px label, a Gold (#FFC20E) arrow '\u203a' (24px) after two non-breaking spaces, sized 248\u00d764px. Section padding 48px 25px 56px 25px.",
  "intent": "Lock the signature CTA banner composition and its element specs.",
  "snippets": "<mj-section background-url=\"...Gradient_callout.png\" background-size=\"cover\" background-repeat=\"no-repeat\" background-position=\"center center\" background-color=\"#faa31b\" padding=\"48px 25px 56px 25px\">",
