  "version": 1,
  "summary": "Gradient Callout CTA: full-width 600px banner, orange/yellow gradient background, headline top-third Brand Blue #00529b Nunito Sans 800 28px center, button below Deep Blue #003D74 fill white 18px Nunito Sans 800 with gold #FFC20E arrow, sized 248\u00d764px, padding 48px 25px 56px 25px."
